<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I&apos;m a professional format editor. I can tell you from experience that the same text translated from English to Spanish takes up more space. Not sure i<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I'm a professional format editor. I can tell you from experience that the same text translated from English to Spanish takes up more space. Not sure if it's because their words tend to be longer, or if it's all the masculine and feminine articles that we don't use in English that add in more words, but there you have it. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
