  <span id="freeText557672833446290499" style="display:none">Hello. I'm Pierce Brown, the author of the Red Rising Saga, a NYT #1 bestseller.<br /> I figured I'd write you myself than have corporate copy pasted below my totally natural author photo. <br /><br />In my books you'll find stories of men and women finding their inner strength when all seems lost. You'll also find me exploring themes of love, violence, hope, and power--what it means, why people seek it, and how they hold onto it.<br /><br /><br /><br /><br />IG @piercebrownofficial <br />Twitter @pierce_brown </span>
